{"pageProps":{"post":{"id":"311","date":"2011. 4. 28. 21:57","title":"왜 사무실에서는 창의적인 일을 하지 않을까?","content":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">//<![CDATA[\r\nwriteCode2(\"<object width=\\\"540\\\" height=\\\"410\\\"><param name=\\\"movie\\\" value=\\\"http://video.ted.com/assets/player/swf/EmbedPlayer.swf\\\"></param><param name=\\\"allowFullScreen\\\" value=\\\"true\\\" /><param name=\\\"allowScriptAccess\\\" value=\\\"always\\\"/><param name=\\\"wmode\\\" value=\\\"transparent\\\"></param><param name=\\\"bgColor\\\" value=\\\"#ffffff\\\"></param> <param name=\\\"flashvars\\\" value=\\\"vu=http://video.ted.com/talks/dynamic/JasonFried_2010X-medium.flv&amp;su=http://images.ted.com/images/ted/tedindex/embed-posters/JasonFried-2010X.embed_thumbnail.jpg&amp;vw=432&amp;vh=240&amp;ap=0&amp;ti=1014&amp;lang=kor&amp;introDuration=15330&amp;adDuration=4000&amp;postAdDuration=830&amp;adKeys=talk=jason_fried_why_work_doesn_t_happen_at_work;year=2010;theme=a_taste_of_tedx;theme=not_business_as_usual;theme=new_on_ted_com;event=New+on+TED.com;tag=Business;tag=Culture;tag=Design;tag=Technology;tag=creativity;tag=work;&amp;preAdTag=tconf.ted/embed;tile=1;sz=512x288;\\\" /><embed src=\\\"http://video.ted.com/assets/player/swf/EmbedPlayer.swf\\\" pluginspace=\\\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\\\" type=\\\"application/x-shockwave-flash\\\" wmode=\\\"transparent\\\" bgColor=\\\"#ffffff\\\" width=\\\"540\\\" height=\\\"410\\\" allowFullScreen=\\\"true\\\" allowScriptAccess=\\\"always\\\" flashvars=\\\"vu=http://video.ted.com/talks/dynamic/JasonFried_2010X-medium.flv&amp;su=http://images.ted.com/images/ted/tedindex/embed-posters/JasonFried-2010X.embed_thumbnail.jpg&amp;vw=432&amp;vh=240&amp;ap=0&amp;ti=1014&amp;lang=kor&amp;introDuration=15330&amp;adDuration=4000&amp;postAdDuration=830&amp;adKeys=talk=jason_fried_why_work_doesn_t_happen_at_work;year=2010;theme=a_taste_of_tedx;theme=not_business_as_usual;theme=new_on_ted_com;event=New+on+TED.com;tag=Business;tag=Culture;tag=Design;tag=Technology;tag=creativity;tag=work;\\\"></embed></object>\")//]]></script></div>\n<br>대부분이 공감할 것 같은 이야기.<br>\n사무실에서는 정말 창의적인 일들이 잘 일어나지 않는다.<br>\n주로 집에 가는 길 차안에서.. 퇴근 후에 소파에 늘어져 있다가.. 화장실에 앉아있다가..<br>\n이럴때 재미난 생각들이 많이 나는 것 같다.<br>\n<br>그래.. 책상에 앉아서인 것 같다.<br>\n사무실을 마음대로 꾸밀 수 있도록 해야한다. 그래야 창의적으로 일할 수 있을 것 같다.<br>\n<br>난 지금 스탠드 하나만 있으면 될 것 같은데.. 그리고 사방이 막힌 공간이랑.. ^^            ","summary":"\n//<![CDATA[\r\nwriteCode2(\"<object width=\\\"540\\\" height=\\\"410\\\"><param name=\\\"movie\\\" value=\\\"http://video.ted.com/assets/player/swf/EmbedPlayer.swf\\\"></param><param name=\\\"allowFullScreen\\\" value=\\\"true\\\" /><param name=\\\"allowScriptAccess\\\" value=\\\"always","image":"https://t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/openGraph/opengraph.png"}},"__N_SSG":true}